{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_08_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 カロリーを消費しないと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "寒さ対策はパーフェクトです！\nさぁ、スタジオに出発です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm perfectly prepared for the cold!\nWell then‚ let's depart for the studio!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今度こそ練習に参加出来そうだな。良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like you'll be able to participate in practice this time. That's good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5313604514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.533765014
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.533765014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "イヤです～！　寒いです～！\n対策しても寒過ぎます～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! It's cold!\nEven with preparations‚ it's too cold!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5643781662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.4620874087
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "カイロがなければ即引き返してました……！\nカイロ様々ですよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I didn't have these hand warmers‚ I would've immediately turned back…!\nPraise be to hand warmers…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2977114995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまでの威勢はどうしたんだ？\nまぁ、ゆっくりでも進んでるからいいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What happened to all that energy from earlier?\nWell‚ it's fine as long as we're moving‚ even if it's slow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5333345413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9493660926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころに外に出てほしいという\n{user}さんたってのお願いですからね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you wanted Kokoro to go outside‚\nDidn't you‚ {user}-san~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3534259796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、さすがにそろそろ……\nあっ、あそこのかまくらで一休みしていきましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bu‚ but‚ we really should be getting going soon…\nAh‚ let's take a little break at that Gamakura over there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3867557526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "街中にかまくら？　……本当だ。観光客向けに\n作ったみたいだな。中でおしるこを売ってるのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A Gamakura in the middle of the city? …You're right. It looks like\nThey made it for tourists. I guess they're selling sweet red bean soup inside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2333238602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.6342300415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "このままでは二人とも\n心身ともに冷え切って遭難してしまいます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we keep going like this‚ we'll both\nFreeze to death‚ both physically and mentally…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4420545578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "おしるこを飲まない限り\nこころは一歩も動けません～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unless I drink some sweet red bean soup‚\nKokoro won't take another step~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1420545578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.7635725657
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。練習の時間まで余裕があるし、寄って行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. We have some time before practice‚ let's stop by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7635725657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.0329765002
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　いいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Is it really okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0329765002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "冗談っぽく言ってるけど、本当に辛いんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're saying it as a joke‚ but it's really hard for you‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8900965769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.6958561818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにはバレちゃいますね\nごめんなさい、寄り道させちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You saw right through me‚ {user}-san.\nI'm sorry for making us take a detour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7678307693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.5474670966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、暖を取りながら、少しずつ進めば\nいつの日かスタジオに辿り着けるはずです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ if we warm ourselves up and keep going little by little‚\nI'm sure we'll be able to reach the studio someday…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6344984532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、時間までに辿り着いてもらわないと困るけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we need to get there on time though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6639298995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― One hour later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.217265153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.3172631185
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.3172631185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした……っと\nやれやれ、随分な寄り道になったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was a good meal…\nGood grief‚ that was quite a detour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8666515987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.1704977592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "もうお腹一杯です……これ以上何も入りません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so full… I can't eat anything more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1704977592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうだ。かまくらでおしるこを飲んだ後\nさらにラーメンまで食べたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's understandable. After drinking sweet red bean soup at the Gamakura\nAnd then eating ramen on top of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6666531246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.11587255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "暖を取りながらここまで来ましたけど\nもう温かいものはこれ以上食べられません～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I warmed myself up on the way here‚\nBut I can't eat anything warm anymore~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4471539339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "スタジオまで後少しだ。頑張れないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're almost at the studio. Can't you push yourself a little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4407490175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1516262294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……でも、それまでこころの体力がもつでしょうか\n……あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… but‚ will Kokoro have any stamina left by then?\n…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2666717848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4065731288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子達、リズノワのこと、話してますね\nこころ達のファン……でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Those kids‚ they're talking about LizNoir.\nI wonder if they're our fans…？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3000086786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.0320610604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_08_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "……あの子達の話、聞きました？\nバイト代とお小遣いを貯めてチケットを手に入れたって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Did you hear what they were saying?\nThey saved up their part-time job money and allowance to get tickets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0000086786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
